pr_body:
The structure now is as follows:
 -- `bench.sh` main script that runs benchmarks
 -- `parse_bench.py` formatter for output for the script ^
 -- several directories (on for each benchmark) containing:
         -- `.lua` script that will be given to sysbench
         -- some script that generates data for the table 
 -- `bench_report.lua` formatter for the output of the benchmarks, needs to be `require`d in every `.lua` script benchmark directories.
